column1: #Text=Fort Walton Beach is a small city in Emerald Coast region of Florida , forty miles east of Pensacola .
#Text=Serves Fort Walton Beach and nearby Valparaiso .
#Text=American Eagle , Delta Air Lines , Delta Connection , United Express serve the airport .
#Text=US 98 connects Fort Walton Beach with Pensacola and Panama City .
#Text=Fort Walton Beach has two main arterials .
#Text=The Miracle Strip Parkway ( US 98 ) travels along the seacoast and through Eglin Air Force Base , and the Eglin Parkway ( Florida SR 85 ) links the city with Okaloosa Regional Airport .
#Text=Indian Temple Mound and Museum , 139 Miracle Strip Pkwy SE .
#Text=Aug-May M - F 10AM-4:30PM ; Jun-Jul M - Sa 10AM-4:30PM , Su noon-4:30PM .
#Text=Air Armament Museum , 100 Museum Dr ( Eglin Air Force Base ) , ☏ +1850 882-4062 .
#Text=Billy Bowlegs Festival , pirate themed street party early each June .
#Text=Antique stores and shops along Highway 98 / Miracle Strip Parkway across from the Indian Temple Mound .
#Text=Ft. Walton Beach has many restaurants , including :
#Text=Anglers by the base of the pier on Okaloosa Island
#Text=Fish Lipz , 203 Brooks St ( off Highway 98 by the bridge to Okaloosa Island ) , ☏ +1850 226-7123 .
#Text=Often have small live bands in the evenings .
#Text=The tasty food and entertaining belly-dancer compensate for rather indifferent and amateurish wait staff .
#Text=America 's Best Inn , 100 S.W. Miracle Strip Pkwy , ☏ +1850 244-0121 , fax : +1850 244-1094 .
#Text=Best Western Ft. Walton Beachfront Hotel , 380 Santa Rosa Boulevard , ☏ +1850 243-9444 , toll-free : +1-877-243-9444 , fax : +1850 243-5445 .
#Text=Holiday Inn SunSpree Resort , 573 Santa Rosa Blvd , ☏ +1850 244-8686 .
#Text=The Ramada Plaza Beach Resort , 1500 Miracle Strip Parkway , ☏ +1850 243-9161 .
#Text=Destin is just to the east on the other side of Okaloosa Island .
#Text=Pensacola is about half an hour to the west .
